metadata.name: Galaxy Blue
metadata.description:
This is the 1st in the World Of Bubbles collection. Its a fun and light hearted collection that brings back the fun times and imagination we had a kids. Did you ever blow bubbles and wonder where they went? Did you ever imagine them flying into space? 

I think we all did at one point in time. Even today, somewhere out there might be a galaxy or planet made up of bubbles or some such thing?
